ygData.messageBody:
Hail all my fellow Rangers. I am a level 15 HEF
on the Brell server. I have spent my last 5 lvls in
Everfrost and am now ready to get out into the world for
some new adventures. I know the area from W Karans and
all of Qeynos to Everfrost but want to see the world.
Any suggestions on a good area would be appreciated.
Everfrost provided lots of ops for money making if you have
not been there its worth the trip and has great
hunting. If you are on Brell send me a tell and we can
swap war stories.<br><br>Keban<br>Ranger of Surefall
Glade<br>15th Season<br>Master Fletcher
